      • fromObject

        public static <T> java.util.List<java.util.List<java.lang.String>> fromObject​(java.util.List<T> list,
                                                                              java.util.List<java.lang.String> fieldNames)
        Prepares the data for a file with a table format by converting the list of objects into a list of rows containing a list of cell values. The first lambda expression maps the helps convert the strings to ints in the list. The second lambda expression maps each object to a list of string values of its fields.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of object in the list
        Parameters:
        list - the list of objects
        fieldNames - the field names for each column
        Returns:
        the rows of the report

      • fromList

        public static <T> java.util.List<java.util.List<java.lang.String>> fromList​(java.util.List<java.util.List<T>> list,
                                                                            java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> indexOrder)
        Prepares the data for a file with a table format by converting the list of lists into a list of rows containing a list of cell values. The lambda expression converts each list object into a list of string values of its elements, in the order specified by indexOrder.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of object in the list
        Parameters:
        list - the list of objects
        indexOrder - the index of the value for each column
        Returns:
        the rows of the report

      • export

        public static void export​(java.lang.String reportName,
                          javafx.scene.control.TableView tv,
                          java.util.List<java.lang.String> fields,
                          javafx.stage.Stage stage)
        Exports the contents of a TableView as a report in a csv file. The lambda expression converts the list of table columns into a list of the text value of all the table columns.
        Parameters:
        reportName - the raw filename of the report
        tv - the TableView
        fields - the list of field names
        stage - the current stage
